<h1>Luvin’ Summer Blending with rajiv</h1>
<p>I'm going to be showing you many different and fun ways you can use a blender—a blender is not just for smoothies! <b>Everyone is welcome</b>: Thursday 2nd July 7.30pm at the Quaker Meeting House, Queen's Road, Leicester LE2 1WP. This is part of a series of events the Leicestershire vegetarian and vegan group organise.</p>
